Available Tools: create_folder | move_file | copy_file | rename_file | delete_file | list_folder
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "path": "string", "destination": "string", "new_name": "string" }
Response Schema: { "path": "string", "entries": [{ "name": "string", "type": "file|folder", "size_bytes": number }], "status": "string" }
---
Question: Show me everything inside the media assets directory to plan the reorganization.
Call: { "func_call": "list_folder", "path": "/media", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/media", "entries": [{ "name": "images_raw", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "logo_draft.png", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 32000 }, { "name": "banner_v1.jpg", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 150000 }, { "name": "temp_upload.tmp", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 500 }], "status": "success" }

Question: Change the name of the temporary upload file to backup_data_2024.tmp for clarity.
Call: { "func_call": "rename_file", "path": "/media/temp_upload.tmp", "destination": "", "new_name": "backup_data_2024.tmp" }
Response: { "path": "/media", "entries": [{ "name": "images_raw", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "logo_draft.png", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 32000 }, { "name": "banner_v1.jpg", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 150000 }, { "name": "backup_data_2024.tmp", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 500 }], "status": "renamed" }

Question: Remove the outdated logo draft since the final version is now approved.
Call: { "func_call": "delete_file", "path": "/media/logo_draft.png", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/media", "entries": [{ "name": "images_raw", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "banner_v1.jpg", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 150000 }, { "name": "backup_data_2024.tmp", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 500 }], "status": "deleted" }

Question: Check the contents of the images_raw folder to identify any corrupted files.
Call: { "func_call": "list_folder", "path": "/media/images_raw", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/media/images_raw", "entries": [{ "name": "photo_01.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2500000 }, { "name": "photo_02.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2450000 }, { "name": "photo_01_backup.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2500000 }, { "name": "thumbnails", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }], "status": "success" }

Question: Delete the redundant backup file photo_01_backup.raw from the raw images directory.
Call: { "func_call": "delete_file", "path": "/media/images_raw/photo_01_backup.raw", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/media/images_raw", "entries": [{ "name": "photo_01.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2500000 }, { "name": "photo_02.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2450000 }, { "name": "thumbnails", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }], "status": "deleted" }

Question: Update the banner filename to indicate it is the approved version: banner_approved.jpg.
Call: { "func_call": "rename_file", "path": "/media/banner_v1.jpg", "destination": "", "new_name": "banner_approved.jpg" }
Response: { "path": "/media", "entries": [{ "name": "images_raw", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "banner_approved.jpg", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 150000 }, { "name": "backup_data_2024.tmp", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 500 }], "status": "renamed" }

Question: List the main media directory again to ensure all recent changes are reflected correctly.
Call: { "func_call": "list_folder", "path": "/media", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/media", "entries": [{ "name": "images_raw", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "banner_approved.jpg", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 150000 }, { "name": "backup_data_2024.tmp", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 500 }], "status": "success" }

Question: Remove the empty thumbnails subdirectory as it contains no useful data.
Call: { "func_call": "delete_file", "path": "/media/images_raw/thumbnails", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/media/images_raw", "entries": [{ "name": "photo_01.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2500000 }, { "name": "photo_02.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2450000 }], "status": "deleted" }

Question: Rename the second raw photo to include the photographer's name: smith_photo_02.raw.
Call: { "func_call": "rename_file", "path": "/media/images_raw/photo_02.raw", "destination": "", "new_name": "smith_photo_02.raw" }
Response: { "path": "/media/images_raw", "entries": [{ "name": "photo_01.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2500000 }, { "name": "smith_photo_02.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2450000 }], "status": "renamed" }

Question: Display the final list of files in the images_raw folder to verify the structure.
Call: { "func_call": "list_folder", "path": "/media/images_raw", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/media/images_raw", "entries": [{ "name": "photo_01.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2500000 }, { "name": "smith_photo_02.raw", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 2450000 }], "status": "success" }

Question: Delete the backup data file because the migration to the cloud storage is complete.
Call: { "func_call": "delete_file", "path": "/media/backup_data_2024.tmp", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/media", "entries": [{ "name": "images_raw", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "banner_approved.jpg", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 150000 }], "status": "deleted" }

Question: Rename the images_raw folder to "archived_photos_2024" to better describe its contents.
Call: { "func_call": "rename_file", "path": "/media/images_raw", "destination": "", "new_name": "archived_photos_2024" }
Response: { "path": "/media", "entries": [{ "name": "archived_photos_2024", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "banner_approved.jpg", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 150000 }], "status": "renamed" }
